name: Promotional Shoot
description:
This is a Service!


If your A Band looking for a Promotional shoot for your myspace/Facebook to announce a new CD or a tour or just want some new pics for a layout.


You will receive digital images for online and personal use







This Service is for Ireland Only!
Shoots outside Dublin may cost a little more

name: Live Shoot
description:
This Is A Service!


Are you a band on tour or even just playing a local show,
Or
Are an Solo Artist/Other doing a show 
No matter how big or smal the place
you can be to get top notch photos

you will recive digital imaes for online o personal use





Price Includes Show Entry!


This Service is for Ireland Only!
Shoots outside Dublin may cost a little more

name: Wedding
description:
This is a Service!


Is your big day coming up, and your looking to catch every second of it?, 
You can be confident you have found a photographer
thats sure to catch every moment of your special day,


You will receive a beautiful book to place anywhere in the home,
for your family and friends to look back on the day and
remember it all.




This Service is for Ireland Only!

name: Family Portraits
description:
This is a Service!

Are you looking to frame a beautiful photo of you and your family?

You will receive an  A2 sized floating Frame, to hang anywhere in your home, And a FREE framed photo to place on a coffee table




This Service is for Ireland Only!

name: Fashion Shoot
description:
This is a Service!

Are you looking to frame a beautiful photo of you and your family?

You will receive any size print you like, for your porfolio and digital images for online use




This Service is for Ireland Only!
